Name:
* Oleksandr Pyatnytsya UKR disqualified for doping. 




Men's Javelin throw - Athletics - London 2012 Summer Olympics
Event Format:
     
     Athletes competed in a qualifying round followed by the final. Top twelve and ties in the qualifying round and all those reaching the announced qualification limit advanced to the final. In the final all finalists were given three tries. The top eight were then given three more. Event facts: Men's Javelin throw competition was held at the Olympic Stadium and 44 athletes participated in the event.
